data.description: Rare one-story newer home with multi-generation living! This home boasts one the best layouts around: open floor plan, spacious foyer, tall ceilings, light & bright throughout!  PLUS, TWO primary bedrooms--one is part of a multi-generational living layout where you have an apartment with private entrance with living room, kitchenette, bathroom & w-d area!  Perfect for adult children, grandparents, or use as a media room! The home has beautiful luxury vinyl plank flooring & neutral colors. The kitchen is open to the living room with a cozy gas fireplace!  The kitchen has shaker cabinets, granite, large seated island, plus a sizable eat-in-kitchen!  One primary bedroom has dual sinks, garden tub & separate shower with a huge walk in closet!  Two other sizable bedrooms & 3.5 baths! Entertain in your private back yard & covered patio! Awesome community with walking trails, catch & release ponds, two pools & parks! Close to shopping, highways & airport! Award-winning schools!
